You would have to:

    Manually create header JSON

    Encode it

    Create payload

    Sign it

👉 With builder ✅
You simply write:

Jwts.builder()
   .setSubject(username)
   .setIssuedAt(new Date())
   .setExpiration(...)
   .signWith(key)
   .compact();

