🔹 builder()

👉 Starts token creation
🔹 .setSubject(username)

👉 Adds user identity
🔹 .setIssuedAt()

👉 Adds creation time
🔹 .setExpiration()

👉 Adds expiry
🔹 .signWith(key)

👉 Secures token (VERY IMPORTANT)
🔹 .compact()

👉 Final token string
